  "notes": "The profilepic section uses a responsive picture element with multiple source breakpoints. When no photo is available, a div.profileinitials replaces the media--image--figure element, showing the staff member's initials. The enlarge button opens the profilepic-modal; ProfilePicModal handles the modal display. StapContact handles the contact dl. The inner info anchor (linking name to profile) duplicates the outer wrapping anchor — both share the same href. The stretched-link class on the h3 anchor extends the clickable area. The stap-contact dl is always present when contact info exists.",
